{"tid":636594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坐至青馬橋落車 的士男客跨欄蹈海亡","createTime":"2018-04-21T04:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T04:52:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"24bacb7630e54f1477a6e74d966c65f3416cb9db","tid":636594,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"凌晨2時許，一名姓文(68歲)男子乘搭的士往大嶼山，的士沿青嶼幹線行駛，至青馬大橋時，男乘客聲稱想嘔吐，姓薛(49歲)司機於是停車。但男乘客下車後，跨過圍欄一躍而下，跳落海中。司機立即報警。<br />\n水警及消防輪到場搜索，約45分鐘後將墮海男子救起，他陷於昏迷，由消防輪送青龍頭碼頭，送仁濟醫院搶救終告不治。警方現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180421/58099507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F58099507&d=sQdzBtL1UQ3B5MZCQ%2FJm3sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=893bf239\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F58099507&h=1c2f23e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180421/58099507</a>"},{"pid":"44d09f640d31f1ee426de7b89beba858a0fa97c0","tid":636594,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b503c3dcd96c512e3d8c38e4ef4e2f262b3b0a54","tid":636594,"uid":5081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"跳青馬真係要好大勇氣<br />\n望落去都驚"},{"pid":"3fdd7f9d7fae7694816c5cc6b8bd8ddd4789b42f","tid":636594,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"2ec58844e0a116b7b8905e66007217efba742b64","tid":636594,"uid":115040,"like":0,"d